snippet: KFC said it would start delivering its buckets of fried chicken to customers in Los Angeles and San Francisco.
abstract: KFC says that for a fee it will start delivering its buckets of fried chicken to customers in Los Angeles and San Francisco; Houston will get deliveries soon, with other cities to follow.
lead_paragraph: KFC said it would start delivering its buckets of fried chicken to customers in Los Angeles and San Francisco.

headline.print_headline: KFC to Offer Home Delivery for Those Willing to Pay More
headline.main: KFC to Offer Home Delivery for Those Willing to Pay More
